Class BasicDataInterceptor

java.lang.Object

All Implemented Interfaces:
DaoOperationInterceptor, ReadInterceptor, WriteInterceptor
public class BasicDataInterceptor
extends Object
implements ReadInterceptor, WriteInterceptor

An example DAO interceptor, mostly for testing purposes but is an ok example of what one might look like, this intercepts DAO operations on GenericTestObject

Author:
Aaron Zeckoski (azeckoski@gmail.com)
